entry.title: Eastern Orthodoxy Gains New Followers in America
entry.content: The church has been attracting more attention from people with no ancestral ties to Orthodoxy, a trend that appears to have accelerated following the outbreak of Covid-19.

entry.title: Young Americans Are Dying at Alarming Rates, Reversing Years of Progress
entry.content: Car accidents, homicides, suicides and drug overdoses have pushed up death rates for children and teens in the U.S.

entry.title: The Offensive Before the Offensive: Ukraine Strikes Behind Russian Lines
entry.content: Kyiv aims to destroy ammunition, fuel and other supplies as it seeks to starve Russian forces in the field ahead of broader ground campaign.
